dcterms:description: A real-world dataset collected from two large supermarket and retail stores in Salt Lake City, UT, USA, containing transactions from August 2018 to August 2019. The dataset includes daily counts of quantities sold for a set of 15 popular beverage products across different regions of the stores.
dcterms:title: Real-world dataset from two different retail stores

dcterms:description: Data from Store 1 and Store 2, which includes the number of regions, products, and time horizon for sales data analysis.
dcterms:title: Store 1 and Store 2 data
